{{Lunisolar September}} 
'''September 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Hōki (era)|ja|宝亀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|770|ja|770th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|September 29|ja|9月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Wake no Kiyomaro|ja|和気清麻呂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , who had been exiled to {{ill|Ōsumi Province|ja|大隅国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , is recalled to the capital following the death of {{ill|Empress Shōtoku|ja|孝謙天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  and the downfall of {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1804|ja|1804th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – Russian envoy {{ill|Nikolai Rezanov|ja|ニコライ・レザノフ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , representing Emperor {{ill|Alexander I of Russia|ja|アレクサンドル1世 (ロシアEmperor)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , arrives in Nagasaki to request trade relations.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1791|ja|1791st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Matsudaira Naritsune|ja|松平斉恒|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 8th lord of the {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  (+ {{ill|1822|ja|1822nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

