* {{ill|Eishō (Muromachi period)|ja|永正|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  15 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1518|ja|1518th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Amago Masahisa|ja|尼子政久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a samurai general (* {{ill|1488|ja|1488th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  or {{ill|1494|ja|1494th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
