'''September 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Hōki (era)|ja|宝亀|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|770|ja|770th year|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|September 29|ja|9月29日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Wake no Kiyomaro|ja|和気清麻呂|12=draft|12=draft}} , who had been exiled to {{ill|Ōsumi Province|ja|大隅国|12=draft|12=draft}} , is recalled to the capital following the death of {{ill|Empress Shōtoku|ja|孝謙天皇|12=draft|12=draft}}  and the downfall of {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|12=draft|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1804|ja|1804th year|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – Russian envoy {{ill|Nikolai Rezanov|ja|ニコライ・レザノフ|12=draft|12=draft}} , representing Emperor {{ill|Alexander I of Russia|ja|アレクサンドル1世 (ロシアEmperor)|12=draft|12=draft}} , arrives in Nagasaki to request trade relations.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|12=draft|12=draft}}  3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1791|ja|1791st year|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Matsudaira Naritsune|ja|松平斉恒|12=draft|12=draft}} , 8th lord of the {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|12=draft|12=draft}}  (+ {{ill|1822|ja|1822nd year|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kennin (era)|ja|建仁|12=draft|12=draft}}  3 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1203|ja|1203rd year|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Nitta Tadatsune|ja|仁田忠常|12=draft|12=draft}} , a samurai general (* {{ill|1168|ja|1168th year|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Eishō (Muromachi period)|ja|永正|12=draft|12=draft}}  15 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1518|ja|1518th year|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Amago Masahisa|ja|尼子政久|12=draft|12=draft}} , a samurai general (* {{ill|1488|ja|1488th year|12=draft|12=draft}}  or {{ill|1494|ja|1494th year|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1624|ja|1624th year|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kōdai-in|ja|高台院|12=draft|12=draft}}  (also known as {{ill|Kita no Mandokoro|ja|北政所|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|One (Toyotomi)|ja|おね|12=draft|12=draft}} , or {{ill|Nene (Toyotomi)|ja|寧々|12=draft|12=draft}} ), wife of {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|1=Toyotomi Hideyoshi|12=draft|12=draft}}  (* {{ill|1548|ja|1548th year|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft}}  2 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1705|ja|1705th year|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Matsudaira Yoshiyuki|ja|松平吉透|12=draft|12=draft}} , lord of the {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|12=draft|12=draft}}  (* {{ill|1668|ja|1668th year|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft}}  5 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1858|ja|1858th year|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Utagawa Hiroshige|ja|歌川広重|12=draft|12=draft}} , a ukiyo‐e painter (* {{ill|1797|ja|1797th year|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

