* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1804|ja|1804th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – Russian envoy {{ill|Nikolai Rezanov|ja|ニコライ・レザノフ|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , representing Emperor {{ill|Alexander I of Russia|ja|アレクサンドル1世 (ロシアEmperor)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , arrives in Nagasaki to request trade relations.

