* {{ill|Hōki (era)|ja|宝亀|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  1 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|770|ja|770th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|September 29|ja|9月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Wake no Kiyomaro|ja|和気清麻呂|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , who had been exiled to {{ill|Ōsumi Province|ja|大隅国|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , is recalled to the capital following the death of {{ill|Empress Shōtoku|ja|孝謙天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  and the downfall of {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1804|ja|1804th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – Russian envoy {{ill|Nikolai Rezanov|ja|ニコライ・レザノフ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , representing Emperor {{ill|Alexander I of Russia|ja|アレクサンドル1世 (ロシアEmperor)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , arrives in Nagasaki to request trade relations.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1791|ja|1791st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Matsudaira Naritsune|ja|松平斉恒|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 8th lord of the {{ill|Matsue Domain|ja|松江藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (+ {{ill|1822|ja|1822nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kennin (era)|ja|建仁|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  3 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1203|ja|1203rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Nitta Tadatsune|ja|仁田忠常|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a samurai general (* {{ill|1168|ja|1168th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Eishō (Muromachi period)|ja|永正|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  15 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1518|ja|1518th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Amago Masahisa|ja|尼子政久|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a samurai general (* {{ill|1488|ja|1488th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  or {{ill|1494|ja|1494th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1624|ja|1624th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kōdai-in|ja|高台院|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (also known as {{ill|Kita no Mandokoro|ja|北政所|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|One (Toyotomi)|ja|おね|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , or {{ill|Nene (Toyotomi)|ja|寧々|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ), wife of {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|1=Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (* {{ill|1548|ja|1548th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
