* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  5 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1858|ja|1858th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Utagawa Hiroshige|ja|歌川広重|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a ukiyo‐e painter (* {{ill|1797|ja|1797th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).

