* {{ill|Hōki (era)|ja|宝亀|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōki (era)|qq=}}  1 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|770|ja|770th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/770|qq=}}  {{ill|September 29|ja|9月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September 29|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Wake no Kiyomaro|ja|和気清麻呂|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wake no Kiyomaro|qq=}} , who had been exiled to {{ill|Ōsumi Province|ja|大隅国|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōsumi Province|qq=}} , is recalled to the capital following the death of {{ill|Empress Shōtoku|ja|孝謙天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empress Shōtoku|qq=}}  and the downfall of {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dōkyō|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunka (era)|qq=}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1804|ja|1804th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1804|qq=}}  {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 9|qq=}} ) – Russian envoy {{ill|Nikolai Rezanov|ja|ニコライ・レザノフ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nikolai Rezanov|qq=}} , representing Emperor {{ill|Alexander I of Russia|ja|アレクサンドル1世 (ロシアEmperor)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Alexander I of Russia|qq=}} , arrives in Nagasaki to request trade relations.

